text:
Worst experience ever.  I paid on time, never was late, but three months into the loan Moneylion reported my loan late to the credit bureaus. 

Called customer service, they confirm I've never been late, but that I'll have to dispute it on my own.  

What?  I'm paying for the membership and your business centers around helping people build their credit and you can't help, when it's your mistake? 

Unbelievable.   Suffice to say, I have paid the loan off early, canceled my membership and will never use them again.   

My credit still shows late 6 months later.   Just submitted the dispute and have screenshots of my payment history.  

Ridiculous  - stay away, it's not worth it.
title: Credit Builder? Think again...Pure Money Grab feeding off those who need help
